<div class="mt-4">
    <h2>About This Library</h2>
    <p>
        PhotoSwipe.Blazor is a comprehensive Blazor wrapper for the popular
        <a href="https://photoswipe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PhotoSwipe</a> JavaScript library,
        providing native Blazor components for image galleries, lightboxes, and advanced photo viewing experiences.
    </p>

    <h3>Key Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Responsive Design</strong> - Works seamlessly across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices</li>
        <li><strong>Upload Support</strong> - Built-in drag & drop file uploads with client-side image processing</li>
        <li><strong>Interactive Controls</strong> - Custom overlay controls with flexible positioning and styling</li>
        <li><strong>Selection & Management</strong> - Enable users to select and delete images with customizable permissions</li>
        <li><strong>Blazor Integration</strong> - Full event handling, state management, and memory cleanup</li>
        <li><strong>Multiple Hosting Models</strong> - Compatible with Blazor Server, WebAssembly, and hybrid scenarios</li>
    </ul>
</div>